/// | 0x1a | 0x60 | 0x601e    | push1 0x1e     |     |      |     |     | 0x1e   | suc | 0      | rds    |
/// | 0x1c | 0x57 | 0x57      | jumpi          |     |      |     |     |        |     | 0      | rds    |
/// | 0x1d | 0xfd | 0xfd      | revert         |     |      |     |     |        |     |        |        |
/// | 0x1e | 0x5b | 0x5b      | jumpdest       |     |      |     |     |        |     | 0      | rds    |
