/// | 0x08 | 0x37 | 0x37      | calldatacopy   |     |      |     |     |        |     |        | cds-32 |
/// | 0x09 | 0x3d | 0x3d      | returndatasize |     |      |     |     |        |     | 0      | cds-32 |
