/// | 0x0d | 0x3d | 0x3d      | returndatasize |     |      |     | 0   | cds-32 | 0   | 0      | 0      |
/// | 0x0e | 0x34 | 0x34      | callvalue      |     |      | val | 0   | cds-32 | 0   | 0      | 0      |
/// | 0x0f | 0x3d | 0x3d      | returndatasize |     | 0    | val | 0   | cds-32 | 0   | 0      | 0      |
/// | 0x10 | 0x35 | 0x35      | calldataload   |     | addr | val | 0   | cds-32 | 0   | 0      | 0      |
